# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/

# OS
.DS_Store

# out/ = Next.js static-export build output (deploy lane, docs/plan-deploy.md) — regenerable, ignored.
# The Python-v1 oracle artifacts that used to live here moved to legacy/activation/oracle/
# on 2026-07-08 (git mv, byte-identical; that folder stays TRACKED as the portfolio demo
# artifact + differential oracle — regenerate with `python3 scripts/run.py --fresh`).
/out/

# Generated convenience dumps — regenerable, not source of truth (artifact policy: ignored).
# RULES_CONFIG_DUMP.txt is a verbatim concat of governance/config files produced ad hoc
# (e.g. to paste the ruleset into another tool); keep it local, never commit it.
RULES_CONFIG_DUMP.txt

# --- Next.js / TypeScript app (the rebuild) ---
# Secrets — never commit a real key (RULES §11). .env.example is the tracked template.
.env
.env*.local
*.key

